                       <div className="flex flex-col items-center">
                           <RefreshCw className="h-10 w-10 animate-spin text-[var(--color-primary)] mb-4" />
                           <span className="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">正在连接高德地图...</span>
                           <span className="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-2">如果长时间无响应，请检查控制台或 Key 类型</span>
